metadata.name: Vanilla Holding Orchid Collective, Series One #1
metadata.description: Hodl and grow with us. This innovative and beautiful NFT project sets a new standard for personal expression and brand exclusivity as its seeds a new expansion phase for world vanilla production in ideal conditions. It grants the hodlers lifetime yearly rewards based on the sale of premium real vanilla to the world markets. This limited and powerful token gives open access to all who want sweet rewards.
